textBox.richText: You know that annoying ad that used to be at the bottom of the homepage? Well, now it’s gone! My Google Adsense account was deactivated!! Yet another amazing thing to happen so far! This really is shaping up to be my year, Isn’t it?! Ohhh yes, I can’t wait to see what’s coming up around the bend! Will it be awesome grades in classes because the classes here are insane? Will something unexpectedly just break for no reason at all? Or will it be just as simple as me casually walking through my room and stubbing (or better yet, breaking) my toe on a chair? Who knows! Oh yeah, and Happy freaking Halloween!!!
